channel.title: [DELTA] My first ever delta source! 317 - 2k + downloads! - 10k+ views!
channel.description:
[center]Well this is my first ever delta source and to be honest I hated it, too many glitches, missing maps and blurr's client was horrible to use. I have now switched to PI and I am enjoying it, alot better than delta, less bugs and loads more features! Anyway on to the main features of this server!
[size=14pt]Main Features:[/size]
[size=18pt]Customized Interfaces for things like, Login Screen, Godwars and Teleports! New NPCs such as, Strykewyrms, Jack Frost and Santa Claus. Full Primal and Primal 2H, FITS THE 317 CHAR PERFECTLY! :D All Chaotic melee weapons! Staff of light with working autocast! (Autocast is horrible on Delta anyway :( ) All 4 Godswords with working specs (AGS spec is glitchy so I removed the GFX from PVP spec, still fked up for NPCs though, sorry :( ) Dragon Claws with Spec! (Spec only hits twice on NPCs, not tested in wildy so I'm not sure!) A nice donor zone with some objects removed and more objects added for space! (A massive cave with some shops, all barrows brothers in lines and altars, Also a tomb that recharges your special attack!) All 3 Strykewyms (Horrible animation's probably mixed in with an NPC in the cache which has been overwritten, nvm though ;D ) Pk Point system fully working and a fully working PVP system with pvp drops and player drops! Pk point shop with customized coloured whips, primal 2h, staff of light, chaotic and energy sword from halo! (Don't ask...)[/size]
[size=10pt]Thats all I can think of without looking at the pics so I will add some more info later ;) Now on to the pictures![/size]
[size=14pt]Pictures: (Some are quite old and need updating but I can't be bothered. Just log into the server to check it out :D )[/size]
